tables.table_schema: CREATE TABLE Vehicle (vehicle_id INT PRIMARY KEY, vehicle_type VARCHAR(255), manufacturer VARCHAR(255), year INT)
CREATE TABLE SparePart (part_id INT PRIMARY KEY, part_name VARCHAR(255), part_type VARCHAR(255), quantity INT)
CREATE TABLE Tool (tool_id INT PRIMARY KEY, tool_name VARCHAR(255), tool_type VARCHAR(255), available BOOLEAN)
CREATE TABLE Material (material_id INT PRIMARY KEY, material_name VARCHAR(255), material_type VARCHAR(255), supplier VARCHAR(255)
CREATE TABLE MaintenanceRecord (record_id INT PRIMARY KEY, vehicle_id INT, maintenance_date DATE, technician VARCHAR(255))
